{
  "stem": "1641.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Anyhow, in the middle of the night-- because we were eating-- we were eating snow all day long.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "That's the only thing which was in plentiful supply, as regards to food is concerned.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So I had to go to the toilet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And to go to the toilet was a major effort, even for a healthy person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And with a person with high temperature, first I have to get out from my bed, with six people lying on me, and around me, and on top of me.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I had to lift up many legs, climb out from the so-called second level of the you know, three-level bed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And then I-- I stepped down and I stepped on three other people, who were lying there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So, you bastard, why are you step on me?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I said, sorry, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then I step on the next one.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "To get off him, I had step on the next person.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And so forth, I had to go through-- I had to urinate a bit on some of the people, because I couldn't hold it back any longer.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so anyhow, I-- I had to do-- this was about-- I had to go about 25 meters, through many bodies, stepping on heads, on stomachs, on legs.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And eventually, with terrific effort, I got out to this half-- it was half outside, half still inside.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was partially covered, this trench where you're supposed to do your job.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as I arrived there, it was very icy-- slippery as well.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anyhow, I fell down, on the edge of the mountain of excreta.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I passed out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I passed out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know I don't know how long I was passed out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I was lying there with my hands and legs hanging into the shit.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
